v1.33 beta13 Wednesday 28 May 2026 PL
It's been a while!

* Sanity checks before upload + better logging.

* Sysop can now disable filetransfer entirely by leaving the defines for
  UPLOADPRGM and DOWNLOADPRGM empty.

* UTF8 in outgoing mail and to usenet - big milestone! Incoming e-mail should
  look decent now also.

* Usenet signature delimiter fixed ("-- " instead of "--")

* Newstoss is better at importing utf8 but still not perfect (how to handle 
  {}| etc I don't know yet)

* You can now browse command history using arrow keys up and down

* Extra check implemented in cmd_post_text and cmd_comment to make sure each 
  post has an empty line at the end (inews likes that better)

* "Ändra plan" was just weird so I aliased that to "Ändra signatur" but kept 
  "Ändra plan" for historical reasons of course. But take note that 
  "Ändra plan" does not change your .plan-file. Something else does 
  (can't remember what exactly haha).

* I screwed up and we lost the ability to show actual number of posts in 
  conferences. Sorry! It's fixed now

* New sklaffadm command "forcepurge" deletes text regardless of "age". 
  Useful when tossing large number of usenet articles.

* Extensive logging and debugging around inews and in other places I can't 
  recall right now :O.

* Fixed lang.h where I accidently used utf8 instead of sf7 (stooopid me!!)

* Hard coded text strings in previous release is now defined in lang.h 
  instead and translated to English

* Mailtoss is now a lot more verbose. Needed it for my own trouble 
  shooting :D.

2026-05-23: Added documentation: Inn NNTP server on Rocky Linux 10. 
